      <description>&lt;p&gt;&lt;a href=&#34;http://www.pitslamp.com/images/blogposts/20130610_nespresso_vanilio_caramelito_ciocatting-1600.jpg&#34;&gt;&lt;img src=&#34;http://www.pitslamp.com/images/blogposts/20130610_nespresso_vanilio_caramelito_ciocattino-1600.jpg&#34; alt=&#34;Nespresso packshots caramelito&#34; /&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

